title: Well Done
description:
Sangwoo Yoon was climbing up the corporate ladder until he got caught sleeping with his boss’s daughter. Two years later, he’s back at the bottom of another soulless gig when he stumbles upon the famous CEO Jaehyun Han in a…compromising position. Now, Jaehyun wants Sangwoo to work under him. Is this the career defining break he’s been looking for, or a trap?
